ustralia chc helicopters africa chc composites gander newfoundland chc ems and sar servicesedit irelandedit chc s operated for the irish coast guard chc helicopter serves as the sole provider of search and rescue helicopter services to the irish coast guard where it had operated a fleet of six sikorsky sn helicopters based in dublin shannon waterford and sligo this fleet has now been replaced by  sikorsky s helibus the sn exited service in december  with a flight from dublin airport to weston aerodrome west dublin the flight was operated by eisar the oldest sn in commercial operation at the time united kingdomedit chc currently provides sar helicopters to two of the four maritime and coastguard agency bases in the uk portland leeonsolent and until recently also operated from sumburgh and stornoway chc as part of the soteria sar consortium was selected as the preferred bidder for a year contract to provide a civilian search and rescue service throughout the united kingdom however days before the contract was due to be signed in february  the british government halted the process after chc disclosed that it had unauthorised access to commercially sensitive information australiaedit chc is the largest provider of emergency medical helicopter services in australiacitation needed militaryedit royal australian air force raaf  chc has been providing dedicated rescue support to the raaf since  where it operates sikorsky s policeedit victoria police air wing and air ambulance services  chc provides three eurocopter san dauphin and one eurocopter ec aircraft plus maintenance services to the victoria police ambulanceedit snowy hydro southcare multipurpose helicopter in australia fire and emergency services authority of western australia  based in perth wa chc provides a bell  ep aircraft ambulance victoria  up until the end of  chc provided two bell ep helicopters for air ambulance and search and rescue duties ambulance service of new south wales  chc provides three aws and two ec helicopters to supplement ambulance nsws eight contracted aeromedical helicopters these are based at wollongong sydney and orange new south wales snowy hydro southcare air ambulance service  chc operates a bell  for emergency helicopter service based in symonston australian capital territory norwayedit norwegian search and rescue  chc provides private search and rescue services in the norwegian sector of the north sea but acts in concert with the norwegian rescue coordination centres the chc sar fleet includes two super puma l and three super puma ec  other related servicesedit nh chc is designing manufacturing and installing  liferaft assembly kits for the nh helicopter a new military search and rescue helicopter provided to the military of several european countries through a joint venture shared by agusta eurocopter and fokker supply rescue and support services chc provides extensive ship supply and rescue service off the coast of africa and the netherlands and helicopter support services to scientific expeditions in antarctica and other harsh environments fleetedit chc operates approximately  aircraft in over  countries which include malaysia australia brazil thailand the philippines the middle east south africa ecuador angola gabon and equatorial guinea helicoptersedit   agustawestland aw   eurocopter super puma as l l   eurocopter ec   eurocopter as n n n dauphin   sikorsky s a and c series   sikorsky s   bell    airbus ec  locationsedit  australia new south wales sydney • orange • wollongong • newcastle victoria melbourne • latrobe valley • bendigo western australia perth • karratha • broome  bangladesh  brazil  canada british columbia richmond delta nova scotia halifax  denmark esbjerg  india  indonesia  ireland cork • dublin • shannon • waterford • sligo  malaysia  norway stavanger • bergen • florø • kristiansund • brønnøysund  netherlands den helder  philippines  scotland • aberdeen • sumburgh  thailand  united kingdom • norwich • humberside accidents and incidentsedit on march   chc sikorsky s operating as rescue  crashed into the sea off blacksod west of ireland  fatalities  missing on april   a chc ec crashed near turøy norway killing all  occupants on august   a chc super puma l crashed  nm from sumburgh in the shetlands scotland the aircraft crashed into the sea killing  passengers and the remaining  passengers and  crew were rescued see alsoedit  chc helicopters eurocopter as crash canadian helicopters chc airways referencesedit  chc group reports fourth quarter and full year  resultsaccessdate   company profile for chc helicopter corp heli retrieved    helicopter firm chc group files for bankruptcy protection cbc news  may  retrieved  june    httpswwwflightglobalcomnewsarticlesmorebadnewsforairbushelicopterssuperpumafami  httpwwwchchelicomnode  httpwwwchccacorporateaboutchcphp  httpwwwairlinersnetphoto  press release soteria sar  february  retrieved  april    uk government shelves helicopter search and rescue privatisation  ambulanceserviceofnewsouthwaleshelicopteroperations  httpwwwsnowyhydrosouthcarecomaupagespageasp  httpswwwnorskoljeoggassnopagefilesunderlagsrapportengelskversjonkorrigertavjanerikvinnempdfepslanguageno  a b   httpwwwthejournaliecoastguardhelicoptermar  httpsaviationsafetynetwikibasewikiphpid  httpwwwbbccomnewsukscotlandnortheastorkneyshetland external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to chc helicopter chc helicopter chc helicopter history canadian helicopters setting the standard by vertical magazine v t e helicopter airlines in operation air greenland air harrods airtransport europe atlantic airways babcock mission critical services scandinavian airambulance bristow helicopters bristow norway british international helicopters caribbean helicopters chc helicopter chc airways columbia helicopters copterline cougar helicopters dap helicópteros falcon aviation services fishtail air global vectra helicorp gulf helicopters heli air heli air monaco heli air services heli hollan